Package: jliwc
Title: jliwc: A Japanese text analyzer for J-LIWC dictionary
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tasuku", "Igarashi", , "igarashi.tasuku@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9432-4425"))
Description: This package provides functions to analyze Japanese text using J-LIWC, the Japanese version of LIWC (Linguistic Inquiry and Word Count).
    The J-LIWC2015 dictionary is developed by Igarashi, Okuda, and Sasahara (2022) <https://doi.org/10.3389/fpsyg.2022.841534>. The dictionary file is available at <https://www.liwc.app/dictionaries> (LIWC-22) and <https://www.liwc.net/dictionaries> (LIWC2015) for academic and university license users (non-commercial use only).
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
